{{Infobox journal | title = Filozofia | cover = Filozofia cover.gif | editor = Dagmar Smreková | discipline = [[Philosophy]] | abbreviation = Filozofia | language = English, Slovak, Czech | publisher = Institute of Philosophy, [[Slovak Academy of Sciences]] | country = Slovakia | frequency = Monthly | history = | openaccess = | impact = | impact-year = | website = http://klemens.sav.sk/fiusav/filozofia/index_en.php/ | ISSN = 0046-385X | OCLC = 643882854 }} '''''Filozofia''''' is an [[academic journal]] of [[philosophy]] published by the [[Slovak Academy of Sciences]]. It publishes articles in Slovak, Czech, and English. The journal's scope includes [[metaphysics]], [[epistemology]], [[history of philosophy]], [[social philosophy]], [[philosophy of mind]], [[ethics]], [[philosophy of religion]], and related disciplines. The journal publishes 10 issues a year (each month, with the exception of July and August). The [[editor-in-chief]] is Dagmar Smreková.
Papers published in ''Filozofia'' are indexed in the [[Arts and Humanities Citation Index]] and [[Research Alert]].
